    <lb n="13"/>ἐν οἷς ἐστὶ κτήνη βο<hi rend="diaeresis">ι</hi>κὰ Παυσ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ε</unclear><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ί</supplied><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ρ</unclear><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">εως </supplied><gap extent="32" reason="lost" unit="character"/><supplied cert="high" reason="lost"> ἡ δὲ ἡμε</supplied>-

    <lb n="14"/>τέρα μήτηρ Ἀσκλατάριον ἐν ῥύμῃ Ψύλλου λεγομέν<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ῃ </supplied><gap extent="30" reason="lost" unit="character"/> 

