    <lb n="18"/>λαχανοσπέρμου ἀρτάβας ἕξ <num value="6"/>. καὶ ὅσα ἐώνημαι καὶ συνεταξάμην ἐπ᾽ ὀνόματος τῆς αὐτῆς συμβίο<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">υ</supplied> 

    <lb n="19"/>μου Χαιρημονίδος δ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ου</unclear>λικὰ <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">σώ</unclear>ματ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">α</unclear> <gap extent="4" reason="illegible" unit="character"/><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ε</unclear><gap extent="1" reason="illegible" unit="character"/><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ν</unclear> τε καὶ Πανχάριον καὶ τὰ ταύτης τέκνα 

    <lb n="20"/>Κοπρῆν καὶ <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">Π</unclear><gap extent="4" reason="illegible" unit="character"/><gap extent="3" reason="illegible" unit="character"/> <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">καὶ</unclear> <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">Θνᾶν</unclear>, <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ἔχειν</unclear> <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">α</unclear><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ὐτὴ</supplied><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ν</unclear> <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">θέ</unclear>λω κυριευτικῶς. κηδεμόνα δὲ <choice><corr>καθίστη-

