    <lb n="35"/>κηδεμόνος οἴνου κεράμια <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ε</unclear>ἴκ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">οσ</supplied>ι <choice><corr>τέσσαρα</corr><sic><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">τ</supplied><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">εσσα</unclear>ρας</sic></choice> <num value="24"/> κατ᾽ ἔτος, οἷς αὐ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">τὴν</unclear> ἀ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ρ</unclear>κεσθῆν<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">αι</supplied> 

    <lb n="36"/>βούλομαι. Ἐπίμαχον δὲ ἐπίτροπον <subst><add place="inline">ἡμέτερον</add><del rend="corrected" status="unremarkable"><add place="supralinear">η</add>με<gap extent="1" reason="illegible" unit="character"/>ερον</del></subst>, ᾧ καὶ αὐτῷ εὐχαριστῶ <subst><add place="inline">εὖ</add><del rend="corrected" status="unremarkable">πυ</del></subst> γενέ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">σ</unclear><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">θαι</supplied> 

