    <lb n="38"/>μου κυριευτικῶς ἃς κέκτημαι περὶ κώμην Σενοκῶμειν <gap extent="1" reason="illegible" unit="character"/><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">δο</unclear><gap extent="4" reason="illegible" unit="character"/><gap extent="1" reason="illegible" unit="character"/><gap extent="6" reason="lost" unit="character"/> 

